about.summary: Miscellaneous functions for SciViews or general use: manage a temporary environment attached to the search path for temporary variables you do not want to save() or load(), test if Aqua, Mac, Win, ... Show progress bar, etc.

Miscellaneous functions for SciViews or general use: manage a temporary environment attached to the search path for temporary variables you do not want to save() or load(), test if Aqua, Mac, Win, ... Show progress bar, etc.

name: r-svmisc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.3" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-svmisc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/svMisc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/svMisc/svMisc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2dd52147981b51a15071b4cd77a87f790edac77bc215dbbea59764bb0a8c73e4

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 2
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('svMisc')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('svMisc')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/SciViews/svMisc, http://www.sciviews.org/SciViews-R
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: 'Miscellaneous functions for SciViews or general use: manage a temporary environment attached to the search path for temporary variables you do not want to save() or load(), test if Aqua, Mac, Win, ... Show progress bar, etc.'
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
